HEADWORD: hand-crafted
<hw>hand-crafted</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>made by hand or by a hand
process. Contrasted to <ant>machine-made</ant>.</def> [Narrower terms:
<stype>camp-made </stype>; <stype>hand-loomed, handwoven </stype>;
<stype>handsewn, handstitched </stype>; <stype>overhand, oversewn
)</stype>]⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> handmade.</syn>⟦br⟧
